  <Content>&lt;b&gt;Hunting Event&lt;/b&gt;

Are you tired of hunting at the same usual place? Do you wish old hunting grounds give more experience and ability points? Are the popular hunting grounds getting over-crowded? If you answered yes to any of these questions, then this hunting event is for you.

